Sinovel Wind Gets Approval to Issue $863 Million of Bonds

-- B y   B a l d a v e   S i n g h
-- 
2011-10-13T01:40:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-13/sinovel-wind-gets-approval-to-issue-863-million-of-bonds.html
Sinovel Wind Group Co. secured
approval from the China Securities Regulatory Commission to
issue as much as 5.5 billion yuan of bonds ($863 million),
according to a filing to the Shanghai stock exchange today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Baldave Singh at 
 bsingh35@bloomberg.net  